    {
     "text": "VSC Status Bin Virginit\u00e9 bit 7: VSC Badge pr\u00e9sent ds support (virginit\u00e9)  bit 6: VSC IsVirginKey (virginit\u00e9) bit 5: VSC Probl\u00e8me de gamme Renault (virginit\u00e9) bit 4: VSC Probl\u00e8me support de badge (virginit\u00e9) bit 3: VSC Probl\u00e8me C\u00e2ble (virginit\u00e9) bit 2: VSC Probl\u00e8me UCH (virginit\u00e9) bit 1: VSC Probl\u00e8me badge (virginit\u00e9) bit 0: VSC TestDeVirginit\u00e9 (virginit\u00e9)",
     "request": "Read_A_AC_General_Identifiers_Learning_Status_(bits)_BCM_Input/Output",
